title: HIKU! Lee Sin Mix | Community Collab

embed.description: Domics and Jomm took Lee Sin's voice and remixed it. Master yourself, master the enemy. Domics: http://www.youtube.com/user/d0mics Jomm: http://www.youtube.com/user/flashj0mm Effects my Miccool Additional Animation by Ehlboy, Shho, Hyun and Marie Lum **Created in collaboration with Riot Games**

body: "Agire con decisione. Domina te stesso, domina il nemico ... E non sprecare mai un istante. H I K U!"
